nodes.text: This individual was a librarian who was captured during a routine police action by CompForce on suspicion of being part of the Rebellion. He was severely beaten by battalion Commander Ivo Laibach until his daughter, in command of a Rebel squad, rescued him and the other prisoners. One of the young CompForcers, Zevulon Veers, healed the librarian with a medpac, and when his daughter took Veers prisoner, he put in a good word for the CompForcer.
